    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Mantissa</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Mantissa_logo_minimal.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/Mantissa_logo_minimal.png/300px-Mantissa_logo_minimal.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"242\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/c/cc/Mantissa_logo_minimal.png 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Mantissa_logo_minimal.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><center>Mantissa's Logo <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></center></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Mantissa</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeremy_Wright&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jeremy Wright (page does not exist)\">Jeremy Wright</a>, written in <a href=\"/Rust\" title=\"Rust\">Rust</a>, \nlicensed under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GPL v3.0</a>, first released in September 2021 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nSupported by <a href=\"/Zahak\" title=\"Zahak\">Zahak</a> author <a href=\"/Amanj_Sherwany\" title=\"Amanj Sherwany\">Amanj Sherwany</a>, Mantissa <b>v3.0.0</b>, released in December 2021, came with an <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a> implementation of a 769 -&gt; 128 -&gt; 1 net topology.\nIn Mantissa <b>v3.3.0</b>, released in January 2022, the net topology was changed due to an inspiration from reading <a href=\"/Koivisto\" title=\"Koivisto\">Koivisto's</a> source code, considering board symmetry. \nNow instead of a 769th feature for <a href=\"/Side_to_move\" title=\"Side to move\">side to move</a>, the new net uses 2 sets of 128 neurons in the hidden layer with mirrored weights to reflect the game from the point of views of both sides. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Board_Representation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board Representation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Features\">Selected Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mantissa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_Representation\"><a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mantissa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Board Representation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mantissa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning#MoveCountBasedPruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Late Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Reverse_Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Reverse Futility Pruning\">Reverse Futility Pruning</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Singular Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Multi-Cut\" title=\"Multi-Cut\">Multi-Cut</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">SEE Pruning</a> </li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV-LVA</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Countermove_Heuristic\" title=\"Countermove Heuristic\">Countermove Heuristic</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mantissa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a> (v3.0.0)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bishop_Pair\" title=\"Bishop Pair\">Bishop Pair</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rook_on_Seventh\" title=\"Rook on Seventh\">Rook on Seventh</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rook_on_Open_File\" title=\"Rook on Open File\">Rook on (Semi) Open File</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Doubled_Pawn\" title=\"Doubled Pawn\">Doubled Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Isolated_Pawn\" title=\"Isolated Pawn\">Isolated Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Backward_Pawn\" title=\"Backward Pawn\">Backward Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Connected_Pawns\" title=\"Connected Pawns\">Advanced Connected Pawns</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Passed Pawn\">Passed Pawns</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mantissa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?t=13339\">New Engine: Mantissa</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeremy_Wright&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jeremy Wright (page does not exist)\">Jeremy Wright</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, September 19, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=78855\">Mantissa 3.0.0</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeremy_Wright&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jeremy Wright (page does not exist)\">Jeremy Wright</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 10, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=78884&amp;start=18\">Re: New engine releases &amp; news H1 2022</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeremy_Wright&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jeremy Wright (page does not exist)\">Jeremy Wright</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2022</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mantissa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mantissa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/jtheardw/mantissa\">GitHub - jtheardw/mantissa: Chess Engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/4040/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Mantissa&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">Mantissa</a> at <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/15</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mantissa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mantissa\">Mantissa from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Common_logarithm#\">Common logarithm from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Significand\">Significand from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mantissa_(band)\">Mantissa</a> - Land of The Living (1992), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/w7TuKpLaEvk?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mantissa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/jtheardw/mantissa/blob/master/logos/mantissa_logo_minimal.png\">mantissa/mantissa_logo_minimal.png at master · jtheardw/mantissa · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NaN\">NaN from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?t=13339\">New Engine: Mantissa</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?